en_194331_1	The Police Media Spokesperson SP Ruwan Gunasekera said that one suspect was also arrested.
en_194331_2	The preliminary investigations revealed that the vehicle was registered under the name of the suspect's wife.
en_194331_3	He was a three-wheel driver.
